.description
Legend of Lothian is an adventure game in the vein of the Ultima game
series.  It was originally featured in the Sep 91 issue of the Jumpdisk
Amiga disk magazine.  You play the role of a humble shepherd who is
summoned to a perilous task when your country's king is bewitched.  You
must set out in a dangerous land to find the clues that will enable you to
revive your king and save your land.  Includes colorful graphics, hordes of
monsters to combat, helpful citizens to converse with, and puzzles to
solve.  
